KOMPOT USER MANUAL: CONFIGURATION

Configuration is done globally for all programs. Those without
global configuration files (such as qutebrowser) have a config
file stored in /etc symbolically linked to the users' directories.
Make sure when adding other such programs the symbolic link is
also added to "/etc/skel".


CONFIGURATION:

./backup-manager.conf					: System backup.
./bash/{bashrc,bashrc.backup}			: Bash config.
./conf.d/{consolefont,displaymanager,	: System font, set XDM.
		  hostname,keymaps}				: Hostname, UK locale. 
./doas.conf								: Auth & auth groups.
./env.d/{02locale,94fehbg}				: UTF locale, wallpaper,
										: See env-update(1).
./fonts/{local.conf,conf.d/*}			: System font extended.
./fstab									: System partitions
./group									: Groups & members of.
./hosts									: Define loopback.
./i3/config								: GUI, colours, keybinds.
./i3blocks.conf							: GUI sys infomation bar.
./init.d/aesthetics						: Sets console colours.
./locale.gen							: Locale values.
./passwd								: Users, user info.
./portage/make.conf						: Portage configuration.
./portage/package.license				: License management.
./portage/package.accept_keywords		: Enables some ~amd64 flags.
./portage/package.{mask,unmask}			: Enables unstable packages.
./portage/package.use					: Enables pack-only flags.
./portage/repos.conf/kompot.conf		: Define custom repository.
./qtbrowser/config.py					: Qutebrowser configiration.
./qtbrowser/css/kompot.css				: Qutebrowser custom css.
./rc.conf								: Disable openRC colour.
./rofi.conf								: Run menu font config.
./rofi.d/kompot.rasi					: Run menu colour config.
./etc/runlevels/default/aesthetics		: Add aesth. to default boot.
./shadow								: Users & user passwords.
./skel/.config/qutebrowser/config.py	: Adds qutebrowser config.
./timezone								: Defines timezone.
./vim/sysinit.vim						: Neovim settings.
./wpa_supplicant/wpa_supplicant.conf	: WiFi saved configurations.
./X11/Sessions/i3wm						: Starts i3 window manager.
./X11/xinit/xinitrc						: Starting programs set.
./X11/xinit/xinitrc.d/90-i3				: Execs i3 window manager.
./X11/xorg.conf.d/30-keyboard.conf		: Sets X11 keyboard options.
./xdg/neomutt/neomuttrc					: Set mail directory.
